---
title: Bistro Truffle Butter Striploin Steak and Mushrooms with Roasted Potatoes and Broccolini
description: Steak and butter... need I say more? This pan-seared striploin gets the royal treatment with a rich, truffle salt compound butter. Chef's tip: take the butter out the fridge before cooking and it'll come together in seconds!
